no.uib.prideconverter.util
Class iTRAQ

java.lang.Object
  no.uib.prideconverter.util.iTRAQ

public class iTRAQ
extends java.lang.Object

A class that lest you extract iTRAQ values for a given dataset. Translated from Perl code from i-Tracker.
